seasons.overview:
It’s a new year and a new generation of dancers in Brat TV’s longest running show, Chicken Girls.

But the high school Varsity Dance Team is no joke, and with a new captain and a lot of big shoes

to fill, our unique group of teens are learning that having to start over isn’t always a bad thing.

10.name: Season 10
10.overview:
It’s a new year and a new generation of dancers in Brat TV’s longest running show, Chicken Girls.

But the high school Varsity Dance Team is no joke, and with a new captain and a lot of big shoes

to fill, our unique group of teens are learning that having to start over isn’t always a bad thing.

episodes.name: Claire’s Hidden Secrets Amid Divorce Drama
episodes.overview: Claire goes to dramatic lengths to keep her friend group together while keeping her parent’s divorce a secret.

episodes.name: Head to Head
episodes.overview: When Simone and Isla find out there’s an open spot on the Varsity team, they go to extreme lengths in order to keep their tryouts a secret from one another.

episodes.name: She Caught Her Boyfriend LYING!
episodes.overview: When Claire suspects her new boyfriend is being unfaithful, she tries to sneak a peek at his phone, risking their relationship.

episodes.name: Crush REJECTS Her for Being Too Short?
episodes.overview: When Aria’s insecurities threaten to ruin her confidence before a date with her crush, Claire and the Chicken Girls take it upon themselves to help her out. But when their makeover leaves Aria more flustered than before, she might just lose her chance...

episodes.name: She Took PILLS To Study!
episodes.overview: When she fails a pop quiz, Simone’s hopes of spending time with her crush on a school trip are in jeopardy. Desperate to be able to focus on her studies, Simone takes a huge risk and buys study drugs to help her with her school work.

episodes.name: Nervous Girl SCARED For FIRST KISS
episodes.overview: When Sara gets invited to hang out with her crush, she pushes aside her anxiety and agrees to go. But when Sara finds herself alone with her crush for the first time, she worries that they might be taking things too fast.

episodes.name: She Used MAGIC on Her Boyfriend, Instantly Regrets It!
episodes.overview: When her long distance boyfriend starts ignoring her texts, Bel consults teen witch Clover to help and Clover does a spell to reveal Bel's perfect match.

episodes.name: Mean Girls RUIN Her Birthday Party
episodes.overview: When she finds out that Kiki’s not having a birthday party, Claire takes it upon herself to throw her a surprise party – only to learn that Kiki’s classmates find her annoying!

episodes.name: Girl Goes VIRAL, Gets Bullied For It
episodes.overview: When Claire’s heat-of-the-moment speech about the misogyny surrounding Halloween costumes goes viral, she starts getting harassed by online trolls.

episodes.name: Chicken Girls’ Secrets Exposed
episodes.overview: When deep dark secrets about the Chicken Girls start spreading around school, the girls turn on each other, thinking there's a traitor in their midst.
